      <container name="Recalling" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="italic">Recalling</span> its resolutions 2004/52 of 23 July 2004, 2005/46 of 27 July 2005, 2006/10 of 26 July 2006, 2007/13 of 25 July 2007, 2008/10 of 23 July 2008, 2009/4 of 23 July 2009, 2010/28 of 23 July 2010, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2012/21">2012/21</a> of 26 July 2012, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2013/15">2013/15</a> of 23 July 2013, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2014/37">2014/37</a> of 18 November 2014, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2015/18">2015/18</a> of 21 July 2015, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2016/28">2016/28</a> of 27 July 2016, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2017/26">2017/26</a> of 25 July 2017, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2018/19">2018/19</a> of 24 July 2018, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2019/32">2019/32</a> of 24 July 2019, <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2020/11">2020/11</a> of 17 July 2020 and <a href="https://undocs.org/en/E/RES/2021/18">2021/18</a> of 21 July 2021 and its decisions 2004/322 of 11 November 2004, 2009/211 of 20 April 2009, 2009/267 of 15 December 2009, 2011/207 of 17 February 2011, 2011/211 of 26 April 2011, 2011/268 of 28 July 2011, 2013/209 of 15 February 2013, 2014/207 of 30 January 2014, 2014/210 of 23 April 2014, 2014/221 of 13 June 2014, 2017/214 of 19 April 2017, 2021/238 of 9 June 2021 and 2022/314 of 16 February 2022,</p>
